      - Visualized trends with matplotlib and seaborn.
    `,
    url: "https://github.com/Ram-Devopss/Python-Bitcoin-Prediction-Model",
    languages: ["Python", "ML"],
    image: "/images/projects/bitcoin-prediction.png",
    date: "2023-05-12",
  },
  {
    title: "HTML-MYSQL-Resort-Booking-Web",
    description: `
      A resort booking platform with HTML/CSS/Bootstrap frontend + MySQL database.
      - Designed responsive UI with Bootstrap.
