    `,
    url: "https://github.com/Ram-Devopss/HTML-MYSQL-Resort-Booking-Web",
    languages: ["HTML", "CSS", "MySQL", "Bootstrap"],
    image: "/images/projects/resort-booking.png",
    date: "2022-11-20",
  },
  {
    title: "Flutter-Daily-Day-Attendance",
    description: `
      Mobile app for tracking attendance.
      - Built with Flutter and Dart for cross-platform support.
      - Real-time attendance logging and reporting.
      - User-friendly interface for students and teachers.
    `,
    url: "https://github.com/Ram-Devopss/Flutter-Daily-Day-Attendance",
    languages: ["Flutter", "Dart"],
    image: "/images/projects/daily-attendance.png",
    date: "2023-02-10",
  },
  {
    title: "Flutter-Agaram-Milk-Dairy",
    description: `
      Dairy management application.
      - Inventory tracking of milk products.
      - Order management and billing system.
      - Developed cross-platform app using Flutter.
    `,
    url: "https://github.com/Ram-Devopss/Flutter-Agaram-Milk-Dairy",
    languages: ["Flutter", "Dart"],
    image: "/images/projects/agaram-milk-dairy.png",
    date: "2023-01-15",
  },
  {
    title: "CHATTER-BOT-ChatGpt-Django",
    description: `
      Chat app powered by ChatGPT API.
      - Integrated Django backend with ChatGPT API.
      - Real-time messaging and chat history.
